* Descargar
https://repo.continuum.io/miniconda/

* Instalar
```
bash Miniconda3-4.3.30-Linux-x86_64.sh
```

* Actualizar
```
conda update conda
```

* Desinstalar
rm -rf ~/miniconda

##remove PATH 
edit: ~/.bash_profile 



###################
Activar ambiente:
```
pip install pyros_setup
pip install catkin_pkg
pip install -U rospkg
```

